# ============================================================================
# S.P.I.D.E.R. — privacy-first .gitignore
# The repo ships the SYSTEM (prompts, templates, reference). It must NEVER ship
# anyone's personal career data or generated outputs. Everything personal lives
# under workspace/ and is ignored. When in doubt, it does not get committed.
# ============================================================================

# --- Personal workspaces & all generated output (the #1 rule) ----------------
workspace/*
!workspace/.gitkeep
!workspace/README.md

# --- The author's own private career system (never publish) -------------------
koushik-docs/
../koushik-docs/
*koushik-docs*

# --- Anyone's source documents (resumes, LinkedIn exports, cover letters) -----
*.resume.*
*-resume.md
*-resume.pdf
*-resume.docx
*resume*.pdf
*resume*.docx
*CV*.pdf
linkedin-data/
linkedin_extracted/
Basic_LinkedIn_Data*/
Complete_LinkedIn_Data*/
*.linkedin.zip
Connections.csv
messages.csv
Invitations.csv
Email Addresses.csv
Profile.csv
Positions.csv
Skills.csv
Endorsement*.csv

# --- Generated personal artifacts anywhere in the tree ------------------------
**/master-resume.md
**/signal.md
**/*-resume-*.pdf
**/*-signal-*.pdf
**/application-log.md
**/linkedin-analysis.html
**/start-here.html
# (Templates and examples are committed explicitly via the !allow rules below.)
!templates/**
!examples/**
!reference/**
!prompts/**

# --- OS / editor / tooling cruft ----------------------------------------------
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*~
.claude/settings.local.json
node_modules/
__pycache__/
*.log
